
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Consumidor as Consumidore/Aplicación
    participant API as API Reversar Compra TC <br> Epica 2677: SBRG_Card_RollbackPurchase <br> HU 58397:  POST - reversal-card-purchase/v1/execution
    participant CL as Caché Local
    participant Lambda as Lambda de parámetros
    participant Lib as Librería Pipeline (ConfigMap)
    participant getTicket as API Get Ticket <br/> HU 58396:  POST - /cards/credit-card-status-retrieve/v1/retrieve-purchase-ticket
    participant recordTicket as API Record Transaction <br/> HU 57727:  POST - /cards/credit-card-admin/v1/record-transaction
    participant registerTicket as API Register Ticket <br/> HU 57729:  POST - /cards/credit-card-admin/v1/register-ticket-payment
    participant Errors as Control de Errores <br> Librería de mapeo de errores
    
    Note over Consumidor, Errors: Flujo Regional (HN01 | GT01) - Consultar Ticket Compra TC

    Consumidor->>API: REST Request
    Note right of Consumidor: body: <br> cardTransactionReference, <br> cardTransactionType

    API->>API: Validar Request
    Note over API: Valida campos obligatorios según contrato OpenAPI 

    API->>API: Validación exitosa

    alt Consulta parametros en caché local

        API->>CL: Consultar parámetros Lambda Parámetros caché local
        Note right of API: Domain: "REVERSAL_CARD_PURCHASE" <br> name: "EXECUTION" <br> country: XRS 

        CL->>API: Obtiene parámetros Lambda Parámetros Cahé Local
        Note left of CL: Obtiene parámetros de regionalización y negocio
 
    else Consulta  parametros en Lambda Parámetros

        API->>Lambda: Consultar parámetros lambda parámetros
        Note right of API: Domain: "REVERSAL_CARD_PURCHASE" <br> name: "EXECUTION" <br> country: XRS 

        Lambda->>API: Obtiene parámetros Lambda Parámetros
        Note left of Lambda: Obtiene parámetros de regionalización y negocio

        API->>CL: Guarda parámetros lambda Parámetros en caché local

    end

    API->>API: Validar Servicio Regional
    Note over API: Usando parámetros de regionalización obtenidos

    API->>API: Validación Regional success
    Note over API: Servicio habilitado para HN01 | GT01

    API->>API: Aplica Patrón Strategy

    API->>API: Evalúa header.sourceBank

    alt If header.sourceBank == HN01 | GT01

        API->>API: Construye Request API Get Ticket
        Note over API: Mapeo: <br> body: <br> ticketReference = request.cardTransactionReference

        API->>getTicket: Consume (HTTPS) API Get Ticket 
        Note right of  API: body: <br> ticketReference

        getTicket->>API: Response API Get Ticket
        Note left of getTicket: ticketStatus <br> ++ 25 campos

        API->>API: Evalúa response API getTicket

        alt If success == false

            API->> Consumidor: Retorna error envíando por API Get Ticket
            Note left of API: HTTP 4XX / 5XX

        else If success == true

            API->>API: Construye Request API Record Transaction - Campo transactionReference
            Note over API: Mapeo: <br> transactionReference = lastDigit(YY) + dayOfYear(DDD) + HH + mm + sequence <br> ── <br> lastDigit(YY): substring(format(currentDate,"YY"), index=2) → 2026 → "26" → "6" | 2031 → "31" → "1" | 2019 → "19" → "9" <br> dayOfYear(DDD): padLeft(dayOfYear(currentDate), size=3, pad="0") → 1-Ene → "001" | 17-Mar → "076" | 31-Dic → "365" <br> HH: padLeft(hours(currentTime), size=2, pad="0") → medianoche → "00" | 9am → "09" | 11pm → "23" <br> mm: padLeft(minutes(currentTime), size=2, pad="0") → en punto → "00" | 5 min → "05" | 59 min → "59" <br> sequence: responseGetTicket.transactionSequenceNumber → "0001" | "0099" | "1000" <br> ── <br> Ej 1 (2026-03-17 09:05, seq=0001): "6"+"076"+"09"+"05"+"0001" = "607609050001" <br> Ej 2 (2031-01-01 00:00, seq=0099): "1"+"001"+"00"+"00"+"0099" = "100100000099" <br> Ej 3 (2019-12-31 23:59, seq=1000): "9"+"365"+"23"+"59"+"1000" = "936523591000"

            API->>API: Construye Request API Record Transaction
            Note over API: Mapeo: <br> posUserData = lambda.POSUserData, <br> numberOfInstallments = lambda.numberOfInstallments, <br> mccType = lambda.mCCType, <br> requestType = lambda.requestType, <br> creditId = responseGetTicket.creditCardId, <br> organizationReference = responseGetTicket.organizationReference, <br> merchantReference = responseGetTicket.merchantReference, <br> cardExpirationDate = responseGetTicket.cardExpiryDate, <br> transactionAmount = responseGetTicket.cashAmount, <br> trackDataLength = lambda.track2Length, <br> trackData = lambda.track2Data,  <br> validationValue = lambda.cardValidationValue

            API->>recordTicket: Consume (HTTPS) API Record Transaction
            Note right of API: body: <br> transactionReference, posUserData, <br> numberOfInstallments, mccType, <br> requestType, creditId, <br> organizationReference, merchantReference, <br> cardExpirationDate, transactionAmount, <br> trackDataLength, trackData, <br> validationValue

            recordTicket->>API: Response API Record Transaction
            Note left of recordTicket: response: <br> posUserData, transactionReference, <br> vpResponseCode, systemAction, <br> reasonCode, statusDescription, <br> validationResult, authorizationCode

            API->>API: Evalúa response API Record Transaction

            alt If responseRecordTransaction.statusDescription == "DECLINED"    

                API->> Errors: Mapear código de error

                Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado

                API->> Consumidor: Retorna error homologado
                Note left of API: HTTP 422: Reversión declinada por reglas de negocio 

            else If responseRecordTransaction.statusDescription == "APPROVED" | "TRANSACTION_NOT_FOUND" | "ALREADY_REVERSED"

                API->>API: Construye Request API Register Ticket
                Note over API: Mapeo: <br> ticketReference = request.cardTransactionReference, <br> ticketStatus = lambda.requestType, <br> authorizationCode = responseRecordTransaction.authorizationCode

                API->>registerTicket: Consume (HTTPS) API Register Ticket
                Note right of API: body: <br> ticketReference, ticketStatus, authorizationCode

                registerTicket->>API: Response API Register Ticket

                API->>API: Evalúa response API Register Ticket

                alt If HTTP Code response Register Ticket != 200

                    API->> Consumidor: Retorna error envíando por API Register Ticket
                    Note left of API: HTTP 4XX / 5XX

                else If HTTP Code response Register Ticket != 200

                    API->>API: Construye response API
                    Note over API: Mapeo: <br> transactionReference = request.cardTransactionReference, <br> valueDate = currentDate(YYYY-MM-DD), <br> dateTime = currentDateTime(YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SS), <br> ticketStatus = responseRecordTransaction.systemAction

                    API->>Consumidor: Response Exitoso
                    Note left of API: HTTP 200: Response Body 
                
                end
            
            end
            
        end

    end
    
    Note over Consumidor, Errors: Flujo Alternativo - Error
    activate API
    alt Exception occurs
        note over Errors: Error Library Handler
        activate Errors
            API->> Errors: Mapear código de error
            Errors ->> API: Retorna código mapeado
        deactivate Errors
        activate Consumidor
            API-->> Consumidor: Retorna error
        deactivate Consumidor
        Note over Consumidor,Errors: Diagrama guía de manejo de errores <br> http://bit.ly/4rpKVIU
    end
    deactivate API